01:54.125 --> 01:55.375
Is your daddy home?

01:56.500 --> 01:57.667
OK. OK.

02:01.458 --> 02:02.542
Mister Aguilar?

02:03.083 --> 02:03.625
Yes.

02:03.708 --> 02:04.458
Giselle.

02:05.125 --> 02:06.542
Founder of “Discover Your Dreams”.

02:07.250 --> 02:08.167
Nice to meet you.

02:08.500 --> 02:10.750
