03:26.875 --> 03:28.042
- Okay.
- Bye, daddy.

03:28.125 --> 03:29.167
Bye, sweetie.

03:30.958 --> 03:31.792
Give me a hug.

03:35.542 --> 03:36.708
See you later, okay?

03:42.167 --> 03:44.042
Take good care of them.

03:44.625 --> 03:45.625
Don’t worry.

04:30.875 --> 04:33.708
Yeah. Let’s see a cute smile.

04:42.083 --> 04:46.208
