28:28.583 --> 28:30.792
Simba? What’s wrong?

28:32.292 --> 28:33.792
My name is not Simba.

28:34.333 --> 28:36.417
Well… From now on, it is.

28:37.042 --> 28:39.667
Ma’am? But my papa doesn’t know.

28:42.583 --> 28:44.083
