29:19.833 --> 29:21.625
On your feet. Come down, come down.

29:22.208 --> 29:23.125
Let’s go.

29:25.083 --> 29:25.875
Go.

29:26.917 --> 29:30.292
Go, go. Go inside!

29:30.500 --> 29:34.333
No! Where are you taking us?
Please, take us home!

29:34.458 --> 29:37.042
Shut up or you’ll get a beating.

29:37.333 --> 29:39.958
No, please! Help us, please.

29:52.167 --> 29:55.542
Help! Please!

29:55.958 --> 29:58.833
Help! Please!

29:59.625 --> 30:01.042
Get us out of here!

30:56.625 --> 30:58.375
